47:40.959 --> 47:44.458
Go to Fenway Park
like you guys,

47:44.458 --> 47:46.792
the Green Monster.

48:04.333 --> 48:06.041
What's wrong, Pop?

48:13.959 --> 48:15.750
Oh, kid.

48:18.500 --> 48:20.333
Oh, kid.

48:24.458 --> 48:25.583
What is it?

48:26.834 --> 48:29.250
[knock at door, door opens]

48:29.250 --> 48:31.667
Hey, Mick?
You got a minute?

48:31.667 --> 48:33.125
Sure.

48:33.125 --> 48:35.542
Come on, guys.

48:38.083 --> 48:40.041
They all had
a very good day.

48:41.750 --> 48:43.291
Dope was easy to move,

48:43.291 --> 48:46.458
