good about it.

48:49.083 --> 48:50.959
God damn.

48:50.959 --> 48:54.542
[cell phone ringing]

48:54.542 --> 48:57.208
You got Mickey Donovan.

48:57.208 --> 48:58.709
[Ray on phone]
I got him out.

48:58.709 --> 49:01.041
