49:13.500 --> 49:14.875
Holy shit. How?

49:14.875 --> 49:18.208
- Who's Terry?
- He's my brother.

49:18.208 --> 49:20.041
That's what I was
doing today with Ray.

49:20.041 --> 49:21.834
You hear that, Bunch?
Terry's coming home, man.

49:21.834 --> 49:22.750
